{"tid":561533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男警涉與15歲女性交　准保釋官允外遊10天","createTime":"2018-02-15T05:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T13:27:04.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3a13f1a48cd9dea753f6a183971a5cc300088661","tid":561533,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"男警於5年前在屯門涉嫌和一名當時15歲的少女性交，事發多年後被捕。報稱警員的涉案38歲被告陳健敏，被控以一項與16歲以下女童非法性交罪，案件今(15日)在屯門法院再訊，被告陳健敏否認控罪，案件押後至4月17日開審，被告續准保釋候審。 <br />\n<br />\n控方庭上指，為免事主尷尬，申請在她作供時加設屏風遮擋公眾視線，及為她安排特別通道出入法庭，獲裁判官批准。控方一度要求法庭額外頒令被告保釋期間不得離境，以確保他如期受審，惟辯方指被告過往的保釋條件未有限制他離境，故早已報團趁審訊前於2月底至3月初外遊10天。最終裁判官要求被告把保釋金由2000港元提高至5000港元，沒禁止他保釋期間離境。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180215/mobile/bkn-20180215113248001-0215_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180215%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180215113248001-0215_00822_001.html&d=%2Ff3dVIMZAgN3cVdO%2BLpXNAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e7765c6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180215/mobile/bkn-20180215113248001-0215_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fbdff7bce12d9a527476d5840cbad5b1af90056f","tid":561533,"uid":28743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"33食15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bdb73e5fcd44ca625605ef623d04db248d143f","tid":561533,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"男警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af021b8004dbc9f768a037dc3769fb4d0488bb86","tid":561533,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"識食喎"},{"pid":"6d1e44b5d38100c40d5e91483e7a3c6c9f7232c4","tid":561533,"uid":90890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"呢10日又可以屌多幾獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講住，我去報名考黑警先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4e60db484f2e8d730be7ce18fa0c85835139c4","tid":561533,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T13:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/1-29-2018/8dky2P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F1-29-2018%2F8dky2P.gif&h=bf23cf58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入球球員：🇺🇾科蘭(傑志)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2018-02-20(下周二、年初五)20:00 亞冠盃 傑志 vs 全北汽車(韓國)\t@香港大球場</span>"}]}